---
import Layout from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import GraphExplorer from "../components/GraphExplorer.jsx";
import { getRequiredPageEntry, getSection, splitMarkdownSections } from "../lib/page-content";

const page = await getRequiredPageEntry("graph");
const sections = splitMarkdownSections(page.body);
const introSection = getSection(sections, "how-to-read-the-graph");
---

<Layout
  title={page.data.title}
  description={page.data.description}
>
  <style is:global>
    body:has(.graph-page) {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(36, 92, 112, 0.18), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(177, 119, 51, 0.16), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fbf7ef 0%, #f3ebdf 48%, #ebdfcf 100%);
    }
    .graph-page {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .graph-page .page-header {
      width: min(100%, 56rem);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      justify-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .graph-page .page-title {
      max-width: 34rem;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 3.6vw, 2.5rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }
    .graph-help-stack {
      width: min(100%, 56rem);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .graph-help-drawer {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.95rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.1);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
        rgba(255, 251, 246, 0.76);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82),
        0 14px 26px rgba(88, 64, 42, 0.04);
    }
    .graph-help-drawer summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #10273d;
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
    .graph-help-drawer[open] summary {
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }
    .graph-help-body {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .graph-help-body :where(p, ul) {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .graph-help-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
    }
    .graph-help-list li {
      padding-left: 0.08rem;
    }
    .graph-mobile-notice {
      display: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(62, 84, 94, 0.14);
      background: rgba(248, 251, 253, 0.94);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .graph-mobile-notice p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .graph-mobile-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      margin-top: 0.85rem;
    }
    .graph-mobile-actions .btn {
      flex: 1 1 11rem;
    }
    .graph-frame {
      padding: 0.22rem;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34, 29, 25, 0.08), rgba(34, 29, 25, 0.02)),
        rgba(246, 249, 251, 0.72);
    }
    .graph-shell {
      --graph-surface: rgba(242, 248, 251, 0.94);
      --graph-surface-strong: rgba(251, 253, 255, 0.98);
      --graph-surface-soft: rgba(225, 234, 240, 0.9);
      --graph-border: rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.14);
      --graph-border-strong: rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.24);
      --graph-fg: #10273d;
      --graph-muted: #5d7083;
      --graph-accent: #2f5c7e;
      --graph-accent-soft: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.12);
      --graph-highlight: #c9913c;
      --graph-hud-line: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.12);
      --graph-hud-glow: rgba(45, 115, 133, 0.18);
      --graph-radius-xl: 20px;
      --graph-radius-lg: 16px;
      --graph-radius-md: 12px;
      --graph-radius-sm: 10px;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-workspace {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 1220px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar,
    .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.95rem;
      padding: 1.15rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-xl);
      border: 1px solid var(--graph-border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
        var(--graph-surface);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82),
        0 18px 32px rgba(88, 64, 42, 0.07);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar,
    .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel,
    .graph-shell .graph-control-card,
    .graph-shell .graph-stat,
    .graph-shell .graph-legend,
    .graph-shell .graph-command-readout {
      position: relative;
      overflow: clip;
      isolation: isolate;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar::before,
    .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card::before,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel::before,
    .graph-shell .graph-control-card::before,
    .graph-shell .graph-command-readout::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: inherit;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24), transparent 38%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0 22px, rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.03) 22px 23px),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.08), transparent 22%);
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.72;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar::after,
    .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card::after,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 10px;
      border-radius: inherit;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.65;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-copyblock,
    .graph-shell .graph-control-card,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel,
    .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card,
    .graph-shell .graph-sidepanels {
      min-width: 0;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-kicker {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--graph-accent);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-title,
    .graph-shell .graph-card-title,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel-title {
      margin: 0.16rem 0 0;
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.32rem, 2vw, 1.74rem);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-card-title,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel-title {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-copy,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel-copy,
    .graph-shell .graph-control-note,
    .graph-shell .graph-footnote {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--graph-muted);
      line-height: 1.72;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-grid,
    .graph-shell .graph-stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.85rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-toolbar-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(210px, 1fr));
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-stat-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(128px, 1fr));
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-stage {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.38fr) minmax(290px, 0.78fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-sidepanels {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-card-head,
    .graph-shell .graph-panel-head {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-pill-row,
    .graph-shell .graph-inline-actions,
    .graph-shell .graph-action-row,
    .graph-shell .graph-token-row,
    .graph-shell .graph-segmented-row,
    .graph-shell .graph-path-strip,
    .graph-shell .graph-legend {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-pill,
    .graph-shell .graph-answer-pill,
    .graph-shell .graph-stepper-value,
    .graph-shell .graph-path-node {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 2rem;
      padding: 0.38rem 0.72rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.16);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(238, 246, 250, 0.84)),
        rgba(250, 253, 255, 0.84);
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.3;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86),
        inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.05),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-answer-pill {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 249, 239, 0.98), rgba(247, 235, 209, 0.9)),
        rgba(255, 247, 230, 0.92);
      border-color: rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.22);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-control-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      padding: 0.95rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.12);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
        rgba(251, 253, 255, 0.88);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-control-label,
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-title,
    .graph-shell .graph-stat-label {
      color: var(--graph-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-select-label {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.55rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn,
    .graph-shell .graph-select-label select {
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.18);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98), rgba(234, 243, 248, 0.9)),
        var(--graph-surface-strong);
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-sm);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      min-height: 2.4rem;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem;
      transition:
        transform 160ms ease,
        border-color 160ms ease,
        background 160ms ease,
        box-shadow 160ms ease,
        filter 160ms ease;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84),
        inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.05),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18),
        0 10px 18px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.08);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn {
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn:hover,
    .graph-shell .graph-btn:focus-visible,
    .graph-shell .graph-select-label select:hover,
    .graph-shell .graph-select-label select:focus-visible {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.3);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1), rgba(240, 248, 252, 0.96)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88),
        inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.04),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.1),
        0 12px 22px rgba(27, 56, 84, 0.12);
      filter: saturate(1.04);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn[aria-pressed="true"] {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(211, 232, 239, 0.92), rgba(186, 216, 229, 0.72)),
        var(--graph-accent-soft);
      border-color: rgba(45, 115, 133, 0.34);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.14),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(45, 115, 133, 0.12),
        0 12px 20px rgba(27, 56, 84, 0.1);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn:active,
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-button:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn:disabled {
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.45;
      transform: none;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn.mini {
      min-height: 2rem;
      padding-inline: 0.7rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-btn.token {
      min-width: 2.55rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-stepper {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend {
      padding: 0.75rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.1);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88), rgba(241, 248, 251, 0.72)),
        rgba(250, 253, 255, 0.82);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84),
        0 10px 18px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.06);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-item {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      color: var(--graph-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-swatch {
      width: 0.9rem;
      height: 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.18);
      background: rgba(215, 226, 235, 0.9);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-swatch.selected {
      background: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.9);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-swatch.eval {
      background: rgba(255, 248, 239, 0.95);
      border-color: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.42);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.16) inset;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-swatch.highlighted {
      background: rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.9);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-legend-swatch.neutral {
      background: rgba(196, 206, 214, 0.86);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-command-readout {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.18rem;
      padding: 0.82rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.12);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(251, 247, 239, 0.96), rgba(242, 248, 251, 0.86)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84),
        0 12px 20px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.07);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-command-value {
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-command-note {
      color: var(--graph-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-scroll {
      overflow: auto;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.1);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.035) 0 1px, transparent 1px 100%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.03) 0 1px, transparent 1px 100%),
        rgba(240, 246, 250, 0.8);
      background-size: auto, 30px 30px, 30px 30px, auto;
      padding: 0.65rem;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86),
        0 14px 26px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.08);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-lattice {
      display: block;
      width: max-content;
      min-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-edge line {
      stroke: rgba(120, 138, 150, 0.42);
      stroke-width: 1.6;
      stroke-dasharray: 3.4 4.6;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-edge text {
      fill: var(--graph-highlight);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-edge.is-highlighted line {
      stroke: rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.92);
      stroke-width: 2.4;
      stroke-dasharray: none;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.28));
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node {
      cursor: pointer;
      outline: none;
      transition: opacity 160ms ease;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node-halo {
      fill: none;
      stroke: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.24);
      stroke-width: 1.4;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 160ms ease, stroke-width 160ms ease, stroke 160ms ease, filter 160ms ease;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node-plate {
      stroke: rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.16);
      stroke-width: 1.2;
      transition: stroke-width 160ms ease, stroke 160ms ease, filter 160ms ease;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node-frame {
      fill: none;
      stroke: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      stroke-width: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node text {
      fill: #10273d;
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      pointer-events: none;
      paint-order: stroke fill;
      stroke: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
      stroke-width: 0.8;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node:hover .graph-node-halo,
    .graph-shell .graph-node:focus-visible .graph-node-halo,
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-hovered .graph-node-halo {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.5);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(45, 115, 133, 0.2));
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node:hover .graph-node-plate,
    .graph-shell .graph-node:focus-visible .graph-node-plate,
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-hovered .graph-node-plate {
      filter: saturate(1.05);
      stroke: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.42);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-highlighted .graph-node-halo {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke: rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.56);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-eval .graph-node-halo {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.48);
      stroke-dasharray: 4 3;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-eval .graph-node-plate {
      stroke: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.62);
      stroke-width: 2;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-highlighted .graph-node-plate {
      stroke: rgba(201, 145, 60, 0.72);
      stroke-width: 2;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-selected .graph-node-halo {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke: rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.84);
      stroke-width: 2.2;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.2));
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node.is-selected .graph-node-plate {
      stroke: rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.98);
      stroke-width: 2.6;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-node-eval {
      fill: #fff8ef;
      stroke: rgba(16, 39, 61, 0.48);
      stroke-width: 1.6;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-formula {
      padding: 0.78rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.12);
      background: rgba(249, 252, 255, 0.9);
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-stat {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.2rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 0.85rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.1);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), rgba(241, 248, 251, 0.72)),
        rgba(250, 253, 255, 0.82);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-stat-value {
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-columns {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-list li {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-main,
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-meta {
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-main {
      color: var(--graph-fg);
      font-weight: 650;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-meta {
      color: var(--graph-muted);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-button {
      width: 100%;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.16rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.78rem;
      border-radius: var(--graph-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.1);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94), rgba(240, 247, 251, 0.8)),
        rgba(250, 253, 255, 0.84);
      text-align: left;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease, background 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84),
        0 10px 16px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.06);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-button:hover,
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-button:focus-visible {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(47, 92, 126, 0.24);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98), rgba(244, 249, 252, 0.92)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88),
        0 14px 20px rgba(19, 38, 58, 0.1);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-button:disabled {
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.55;
      transform: none;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-table th,
    .graph-shell .graph-table td {
      padding: 0.48rem 0.18rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(33, 65, 95, 0.08);
      text-align: left;
      color: var(--graph-fg);
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-table th {
      color: var(--graph-muted);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-table tr.is-active td {
      color: var(--graph-accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .graph-shell .graph-path-strip {
      padding: 0.2rem 0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 1020px) {
      .graph-shell .graph-stage {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .graph-mobile-notice {
        display: block;
      }
      .graph-shell .graph-toolbar,
      .graph-shell .graph-canvas-card,
      .graph-shell .graph-panel {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: var(--graph-radius-lg);
      }
      .graph-shell .graph-neighbor-columns {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <Nav />

  <main class="page essay-page graph-page">
    <header class="essay-header page-header">
      {page.data.eyebrow && <span class="page-eyebrow">{page.data.eyebrow}</span>}
      <h1 class="page-title">{page.data.title}</h1>
      {page.data.lede && <p class="page-lede">{page.data.lede}</p>}
    </header>

    <div class="graph-mobile-notice" role="note">
      <p>The graph explorer is the widest surface on the site. On a smaller screen, it helps to start with the guide below or use the grid first, then come back here when you want the lattice view.</p>
      <div class="graph-mobile-actions">
        <a href="#explore" class="btn ghost">Open the graph</a>
        <a href="/grid" class="btn secondary">Try the grid first</a>
        <a href="/memo/data-counterfactuals" class="btn ghost">Read the memo first</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="graph-help-stack" aria-label="Graph page guide">
      <details class="graph-help-drawer">
        <summary>What scenario are we simulating here?</summary>
        <div class="graph-help-body">
          <p>We are still imagining one model builder working inside a tiny universe of possible data items or slices named A, B, C, D, and so on.</p>
          <p>Each node is one possible training world. The graph view then holds one evaluation slice fixed while you move through those possible training worlds.</p>
          <p>The point is not realism. It is to make the neighborhood structure visible enough that you can see how local counterfactual edits connect into paths and layers.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="graph-help-drawer">
        <summary>How to read the graph?</summary>
        <div class="graph-help-body" set:html={introSection.html}></div>
      </details>

      <details class="graph-help-drawer">
        <summary>How to interact with this page</summary>
        <div class="graph-help-body">
          <p>Start by choosing a graph lens, a score rule, a training world, and an evaluation slice. Then click nodes or use the quick actions to move through nearby training sets.</p>
          <p>The lens panel and neighbor lists stay tied to that same selected node, so you can inspect one-step deletions, additions, paths, and averages without losing your place.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="graph-help-drawer">
        <summary>What are all the ML concepts we can explore with this graph?</summary>
        <div class="graph-help-body">
          <p>The graph view supports local ablations, coordinated data strikes, Shapley-style sweeps across edges, and scaling layers over the subset lattice.</p>
          <ul class="graph-help-list">
            <li><code>Ablation</code> reads one-step removals from the selected training world.</li>
            <li><code>Data strike path</code> shows coordinated deletions as a path through the lattice.</li>
            <li><code>Shapley sweep</code> highlights the before-and-after edge pairs used to average one contributor's value.</li>
            <li><code>Scaling layer</code> groups nodes by training-set size so you can compare whole lattice layers at once.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card graph-frame" id="explore" aria-label="Explore">
      <div class="graph-shell">
        <GraphExplorer client:load />
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
